==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nettles
<hw>Net"tles</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Knittle</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>The halves
of yarns in the unlaid end of a rope twisted for pointing or
grafting.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>Small lines used to sling hammocks
under the deck beams.</def> <sd>(c)</sd> <def>Reef points.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nettlesome</ent>⟦br⟧
